title: 820-00165 No Audio
message:
Stuck on this one, used known good DCboard+ribbon cable (6 different ones) and still no audio, nothing shown in system profiler for audio. Using volume buttons shows no audio.

Board was Liquid damaged, went thru USC all good minus this annoying problem, this is definitely a board problem. J9500 looks like new.

SMC + Pram Reset no change, Boot with different OSes no change.

Any leads would be appreciated.

title: 820-00165 No Audio
message: Check diode mode on all HDA pins on J9500, 5 pins in total. Also pin 12 and 14.

title: 820-00165 No Audio
message: That seems fine. 1.5V and 3V on pin 7 and 9 making it to the IO board? Also pin 30 diode mode?
